{"tid":727613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去年《香港我家》　今年變《共同家園》","createTime":"2018-07-03T07:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T07:14:20.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6d64d8fee3a013627eeadb65e7501316e974b92c","tid":727613,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/36330950_1739971349421811_5981379208272674816_n.png?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=7eaaeb6ffa1a3d247339183382980c38&amp;oe=5BB0C630\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F36330950_1739971349421811_5981379208272674816_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D7eaaeb6ffa1a3d247339183382980c38%26oe%3D5BB0C630&h=2883c846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年 7 月，政府推出回歸 20 周年主題曲，名為《香港我家》，本地歌手李克勤、楊千嬅及8位年輕歌手大唱「因此知道珍惜我的香港」。<br />\n<br />\n今年 7 月，為推廣粵港澳大灣區發展，香港各界慶典委員會、香港匯演藝能發展中心、廣東省青年聯合會邀請譚詠麟、容祖兒、李克勤等香港歌手，唱出大灣區發展主題曲，名為《共同家園》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65516df247f603d5e04cddb8707b9532d118e45","tid":727613,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:08:55.000Z","msg":"永遠跟黨走"},{"pid":"b4a189eea1b9eed0e463f42a167c414937c5af62","tid":727613,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:13:13.000Z","msg":"有新任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebddd932b570c3ec2f60713c4099e8b3c696b815","tid":727613,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"